'''波斯托伊納洞'''（{{lang-sl|Postojnska jama}}；{{lang-de|Adelsberger Grotte}}；{{lang-it|Grotte di Postumia}}）是位於[[斯洛維尼亞|斯洛維尼亞]][[波斯托伊納|波斯托伊納]]近郊的一個鐘乳洞。波斯托伊納洞洞窟群的長度達21,120米，是斯洛維尼亞第二大洞窟群<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.delo.si/novice/slovenija/nov-najdaljsi-jamski-sistem-je-pod-migovcem.html |title=Nov najdaljši jamski sistem je pod Migovcem |language=sl |trans_title=The New Longest Cave System Is Under Migovec |newspaper=Delo.si |date=16 August 2012 |publisher=Delo, d. d. |issn=1854-6544 |first=Blaž |last=Močnik |accessdate=2015-10-05 |archive-date=2018-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180720141334/https://www.delo.si/novice/slovenija/nov-najdaljsi-jamski-sistem-je-pod-migovcem.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是斯洛維尼亞主要旅遊景點<ref name="DEDI298">{{cite encyclopedia |url=http://www.dedi.si/dediscina/83-postojnski-jamski-sistem |title=Postojnski jamski sistem |trans_title=Postojna Cave System |encyclopedia=Enciklopedija naravne in kulturne dediščine na Slovenskem – DEDI [Encyclopedia of Natural and Cultural Heritage in Slovenia] |first1=Janja |last1=Kogovšek |first2=Tanja |last2=Pipan |first3=Šebela |last3=Stanka |first4=Nadja |last4=Zupan Hajna |editor1-first=Mateja |editor1-last=Šmid Hribar |editor2-first=Gregor |editor2-last=Golež |editor3-first=Dan |editor3-last=Podjed |editor4-first=Drago |editor4-last=Kladnik |editor5-first=Bojan |editor5-last=Erhartič |editor6-first=Primož |editor6-last=Pavlin |editor7-first=Jerele |editor7-last=Ines |accessdate=14 August 2012 |language=sl |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327135823/http://www.dedi.si/dediscina/83-postojnski-jamski-sistem |archive-date=2019-03-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
